quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,Twa Ha
  20,2,(Yewe Muhamadi) ntabwo twaguhishuriye Qur’an kugira ngo ikubere umuzigo
  20,3,Ahubwo (twayihishuye kugira ngo ibe) urwibutso kuri ba bandi bagandukira Allah
  20,4,(Iyo Qur’an) yahishuwe iturutse ku waremye isi n’ibirere bihanitse
  20,5,(Allah) Nyirimpuhwe uganje hejuru ya Ar’shi
  20,6,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi, n’ibiri hagati yabyo ndetse n’ibiri munsi y’ubutaka ni ibye"
  20,7,"Kandi n’ubwo warangurura ijwi (cyangwa ukavuga bucece, byose ni kimwe kuko) mu by’ukuri (Allah) azi amabanga ndetse n’ibyihishe cyane (kurenza ayo mabanga)"
  20,8,Allah! Nta yindi mana iriho ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse We. Afite amazina meza
  20,9,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) waba waragezweho n’inkuru ya Musa
  20,10,"Ubwo yabonaga umuriro nuko akabwira ab’iwe ati “Mugume aha! Mu by’ukuri ndabutswe umuriro, hari ubwo nabazaniraho igishirira, cyangwa kuri uwo muriro nkahasanga uwatuyobora (inzira).”"
  20,11,"Nuko awugezeho, yumva ijwi rimuhamagara riti “Yewe Musa!”"
  20,12,"“Mu by’ukuri ndi Nyagasani wawe, bityo kwetura inkweto zawe kuko uri mu kibaya gitagatifu cya Tuwa”"
  20,13,"“Kandi nagutoranyije (ngo ube intumwa). Bityo, tega amatwi ibyo uhishurirwa”"
  20,14,"Mu by’ukuri ndi Allah! Nta yindi mana iriho ikwiye gusengwa itari Njye. Bityo, jya ungaragira kandi unahozeho iswala kugira ngo unyibuke"
  20,15,Mu by’ukuri imperuka izaba. Nayihishe (ibiremwa byose) kugira ngo buri muntu azahemberwe umuhate we
  20,16,"Bityo, uramenye umuntu utayemera (imperuka) agakurikira ibyo umutima we ukunda, ntazakubuze kuyemera bitazakuviramo kurimbuka"
  20,17,"(Allah aramubaza ati) “Ese icyo ni iki kiri mu kuboko kwawe kw’iburyo, yewe Musa?”"
  20,18,"(Musa) aravuga ati “Ni inkoni yanjye nishingikiriza, nkanayimanuza amababi y’ibiti ngaburira intama zanjye, kandi mfite n’ibindi nyikoresha.”"
  20,19,"(Allah) aravuga ati “Yinage hasi, yewe Musa!”"
  20,20,"Nuko ayinaga hasi, ihita ihinduka inzoka ikururuka"
  20,21,(Allah) aravuga ati “Yifate kandi ntutinye! Turongera tuyigire (inkoni) nk’uko yari imeze”
  20,22,"“Unashyire ukuboko kwawe mu kwaha, kuravamo kurabagirana bidatewe n’uburwayi; icyo kiraba ari ikindi gitangaza”"
  20,23,“(Ibyo) ni ukugira ngo tukwereke bimwe mu bitangaza byacu bihambaye”
  20,24,(Allah aramubwira ati) “Jya kwa Farawo (umuhamagarire kwemera Allah). Mu by’ukuri akabije kwigomeka.”